description:
Tamer12345. If you're reading this, know that there is a great battle coming that will decide the fate of the world. The prohecy tells of this. Bartleby and Sonic are the key to saving the world. We wish we could. tell you more about it bt that will have to wait until we meet face to face. We can't risk telling you what it is in this video in case anybody from the enemy side finds it. We have to go now. We are currently in a car fleeing from about 10-15 cars that are chasing after us. We'll send you a message soon when we can get to safety.

-Love, Sportacs, Obi-wan, and Anakin.

You guys don't want to run into anymore dark warriors.
